text: This company is excellent to talk to and deal with , they are the only company could find to get a dash board Matt for a new model car the Haval H2 model it took 14days to make from the time l ordered and payed for it l was notified that mat was at their store and was sending it to me in Vitoria last week of February 17 very happy dealing with this company and will be dealing with them in future lhave notified Havel dealer of this company Berwick Havel Hallam vic yours truly Ray
